Subject: [FD] Zenario v7.6 CMS - SQL Injection Web Vulnerability

Document Title:
===============
Zenario v7.6 CMS - SQL Injection Web Vulnerability


References (Source):
====================
https://www.vulnerability-lab.com/get_content.php?id=2043


